// IMPORTANT NOTES:
// 1. The 'bannerVideo' field is OPTIONAL
// 2. If 'bannerVideo' is not provided, the 'bannerImage' is used instead
// 3. This ensures backward compatibility with existing player data

// VIDEO REQUIREMENTS:
// - Format: MP4 (H.264 codec)
// - File size: 2-4 MB recommended (max 8 MB)
// - Duration: 8-15 seconds (loops)
// - Resolution: 1920x1080 or 1280x720
// - No audio (video is muted)

// FILE PLACEMENT:
// Place video files in: public/assets/videos/players/
// Example path: public/assets/videos/players/anthony-edwards-banner.mp4

// TO ADD A VIDEO:
// 1. Create the video file and place it in public/assets/videos/players/
// 2. Update the JSON: add "bannerVideo": "/assets/videos/players/filename.mp4"
// 3. No code changes needed - the component handles both video and image

// To generate optimized videos from existing files, see:
// - BANNER_VIDEO_SETUP.md for FFmpeg compression commands
// - https://ffmpeg.org/documentation.html
